parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Failure of the front suspension can cause loss of control, accidents, and injuries.
symptoms: Vibrations while driving
uneven tire wear
clunking or popping noises from the front end
wheel bearings or ball joints failing
and difficulty steering.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Failure of the ball joints can cause loss of control, accidents, and injuries.
symptoms: Clunking or popping noises from the front end
uneven tire wear
vibrations while driving
and difficulty steering.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Failure of the hub assembly can cause loss of control, accidents, and injuries.
symptoms: Vibrations while driving
uneven tire wear
clunking or popping noises from the front end
and difficulty steering.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The sudden stalling or shut-off of the engine can lead to accidents, especially when driving at high speeds or in heavy traffic.
symptoms: The engine stalls or shuts off without warning
often accompanied by a loss of power steering and brakes. The vehicle may not restart immediately
leaving the driver stranded.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Oil sludge build-up can cause engine failure, leading to costly repairs and potentially dangerous driving conditions.
symptoms: Oil sludge build-up in the engine
often accompanied by loud engine knocking or rattling noises.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: PCM failure can cause the engine to stall or shut off, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: The PCM overheats
causing the engine to stall or shut off. This may be accompanied by a "NO BUS" warning on the odometer.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Malfunctioning air conditioning can cause discomfort and distraction while driving, potentially leading to accidents.
symptoms: The air conditioning system malfunctions
often causing the fan motor to turn on and off randomly.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Transmission failure can cause the vehicle to stall or lose power, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: The transmission slips or hesitates
the vehicle hesitates before accelerating
the transmission drops from high gear to low gear
the vehicle loses power
the transmission makes a loud noise
the vehicle will not shift into gear.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Rear differential failure can cause the vehicle to lose control, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: A loud humming noise coming from the rear differential
the rear differential fails
the vehicle vibrates while driving.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Clutch failure can cause the vehicle to stall or lose power, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: The clutch pedal feels soft or spongy
the clutch pedal sticks to the floor
the clutch pedal does not return to its normal position.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Transfer case failure can cause the vehicle to lose power or become stuck in four-wheel drive, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: The transfer case fails to shift from four-wheel high to two-wheel drive
the vehicle becomes stuck in four-wheel drive.
